title: Corinthiax
lyrics:
No body, so no shadows where I stand
Different kind of blood, in my mouth is a gem
I'm more than man
In my heart and eyes, there's a pain
Tension's building in these bands again
It's official

You're listening to Wicca Phase Springs Eternal

GothBoiClique



Esoteric god, Aramaic texts

Lighting candles up

Make a pact while you light another cigarette

Shadows cast on walls

I project my second body as a silhouette



I reach out to her and I call her by her name

Corinthiax, I'll see you soon

The dark manifestation

Of a love that I was given

From a hollow moon

She said she's a bad one, always on attack, now I call for you

GothBoiClique

Even though these feelings come in waves

Stemmed from sacred texts

I reach out to her and I call her by her name

Corinthiax, Corinthiax

Yes, she is a bad one, but I got her back

Corinthiax, Corinthiax

I call out to her, she tenses up and retracts

Corinthiax, Corinthiax

Yes, she is a bad one, but I got her back
